name: Compare 2 Filemaker databases
body:
### Compare 2 Filemaker Databases
With this you can quickly compare 2 Filemaker databases with the same layout. Currently this only echo's out the differences.  Feel free to make any suggestions if you'd like to see something added or changed.

### Special Thanks
A Huge Thanks to Stephan Miller (@eristoddle) for finding and modifying for better, the Python Filemaker API script (fmkr.py) used in this project.
tagline: This shows the differences between 2 FileMaker Databases.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
